      "segments": [
        "s2",
        "s3"
      ],
      "start": 18.75,
      "text": "Geopolitical tensions remain high as Israel and Lebanon move toward a potential ceasefire, with reports indicating that both parties are negotiating a deal to end hostilities. However, the stability of the region is further complicated by North Korea's continued missile tests and the ongoing conflict in Ukraine."
    },
